That website is a good resource.  Scroll down to where it says Class Areas on the left navigation panel, click on the class you're interested in, and check the Creation Guide.  This gives you a little information about the role of the class, the races you can choose to play it, and the statistics important to it. <p><div align="center"><center><img src="http://www.members.shaw.ca/vae/velsig.jpg"><BR>
